</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1458,2501,1206,1235]" pageId="90" pageNumber="369" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="90.[1456,2666,300,1513]" box="[1458,2501,1206,1235]" pageId="90" pageNumber="369">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1458,1593,1206,1235]" pageId="90" pageNumber="369">Breeding.</emphasis>
Breeding season occurs in June-August. Litters have 3-5 young.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1457,2480,1242,1275]" pageId="90" pageNumber="369" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="90.[1456,2666,300,1513]" box="[1457,2480,1242,1275]" pageId="90" pageNumber="369">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1457,1692,1242,1275]" pageId="90" pageNumber="369">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Mexican Harvest Mouse is nocturnal and arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
